data.description: Welcome home!  Price dropped to sell.  Here is your charming, 3-bedroom 2-bathroom Lexington County home.  It has a shed and a large backyard with a nice size pet area.  Close to Midlands Tech, community baseball complex, soccer sports complex, shopping, Columbia Metropolitan Airport, I-20 & I-26, and Hwy 1 to Lexington and to Columbia.  The University of South Carolina is just minutes away.  This is a great home for a STR (short-term rental) or to just make it your own home sweet home to enjoy. Call agent and come see it!
